Package: MixedPsy
Title: Statistical Tools for the Analysis of Psychophysical Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alessandro", "Moscatelli", email = "moskante@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Priscilla", "Balestrucci", role = "aut"))
Description: A package for the analysis of psychophysical data in R. The package allows to estimate the PSE/JND 
    (either from a GLM/psychometric function or from a GLMM), plot the fitted models and 
    the binomial data, simulate psychometric functions of a given shape and data sets.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
  beepr,
  boot,
  brglm,
  lme4,
  Matrix,
  mnormt
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
License: GPL 3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
